{
  "message": "feat(gui): bundle default fonts and enable vendor-font features (ft-1memj.3)\n\n- Copy 33 font files (JetBrains Mono, Roboto, Noto Emoji, Nerd Font Symbols)\n  from legacy_wezterm/assets/fonts/ to frankenterm/assets/fonts/\n- Enable vendor-jetbrains, vendor-roboto, vendor-noto-emoji, vendor-nerd-font-symbols\n  features on wezterm-font workspace dep\n- GUI binary now launches with default font when no user config is present\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
